    "body": "These are currently skipped, because `pycapnp` isn't installed (https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/actions/runs/26943765833/job/79499532298#step:10:4286):\r\n```bash\r\ninterface_ipc.py                                                                 | ○ Skipped | 0 s\r\ninterface_ipc_mining.py                                                          | ○ Skipped | 0 s\r\n```\r\nThey seem to work fine locally. Not sure if this was missed, or on purpose.",
